{
    "publish_date": "2014-11-18T17:51:02.000Z", 
    "score": 3.654903967398256e-05, 
    "video_length": "PT5M3S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "My plan for my life was to\nhave a child every two years.", 
            "dur": "2.754", 
            "start": "53.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had that mapped out.", 
            "dur": "0.916", 
            "start": "56.314"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was going to have a\nkid every two years.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "57.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I didn&#39;t know how many.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "58.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I wanted a big family.", 
            "dur": "1.24", 
            "start": "60.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we had a boy first, and then\ntwo years later another boy.", 
            "dur": "4.27", 
            "start": "61.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And at 22 months old,\nwe found a tumor.", 
            "dur": "5.55", 
            "start": "65.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Suddenly we were thrown into\na whole different world,", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "74.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a world I didn&#39;t\neven know existed.", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "76.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We were thrown into\nthe medical world,", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "78.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into surgery, into the\nhospital, into chemotherapy.", 
            "dur": "6.25", 
            "start": "81.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had my daughter\nright before we", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "87.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "found his tumor, one week\nbefore we found his tumor.", 
            "dur": "3.83", 
            "start": "90.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He had this rare disorder.", 
            "dur": "2.2", 
            "start": "94.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;d ever heard of it.", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "96.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know, there was nothing\nmore that could be done.", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "97.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He did pass away at home.", 
            "dur": "1.625", 
            "start": "99.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the meantime,\nwe had another son.", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "105.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It started with my daughter.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "108.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She got to bone\ncancer on her rib.", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "109.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My husband got thyroid\ncancer, and then he", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "111.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "got Burkitt&#39;s lymphoma.", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "114.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve never seen\nchemotherapy that tough.", 
            "dur": "4.22", 
            "start": "116.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Drew got bone cancer,\njust like his sister.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "120.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was more intense this time.", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "123.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then Andrea got cancer\nfrom her chemotherapy.", 
            "dur": "4.37", 
            "start": "125.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She needed a stem\ncell transplant.", 
            "dur": "1.83", 
            "start": "129.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My husband was diagnosed with\nthe same thing as my daughter.", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "131.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Andrea recovered very quickly.", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "134.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Drew kept getting bad news\nand bad news and bad news.", 
            "dur": "5.63", 
            "start": "136.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My son passed away three\nweeks before my husband.", 
            "dur": "3.475", 
            "start": "142.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I began to think maybe\nI couldn&#39;t do this.", 
            "dur": "5.64", 
            "start": "165.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe I wasn&#39;t strong enough.", 
            "dur": "3.66", 
            "start": "171.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I began to think\nthat I might fail,", 
            "dur": "3.225", 
            "start": "175.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the Lord was not\ngoing to allow me to fail.", 
            "dur": "4.315", 
            "start": "178.445"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I know that that&#39;s\nnot unique to me,", 
            "dur": "4.1", 
            "start": "182.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that He does that for everybody.", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "186.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s not always about us.", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "189.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re not going through this\nbecause we need to change", 
            "dur": "4.08", 
            "start": "191.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or we&#39;re not good enough.", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "195.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I became someone more\ncapable of helping others", 
            "dur": "5.79", 
            "start": "197.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and of having compassion\nand of understanding", 
            "dur": "4.46", 
            "start": "202.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at an intimate level what\nother people go through.", 
            "dur": "4.22", 
            "start": "207.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I found a great\ndeal of joy in using", 
            "dur": "3.26", 
            "start": "211.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the things that I&#39;ve learned\nto help other people,", 
            "dur": "5.12", 
            "start": "214.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "especially families who\nhave children with cancer.", 
            "dur": "3.43", 
            "start": "219.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One of my missions in\nlife is to comfort others", 
            "dur": "3.33", 
            "start": "223.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who are going through cancer.", 
            "dur": "2.012", 
            "start": "226.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that I know how to do it\nbecause I&#39;ve been through it.", 
            "dur": "4.898", 
            "start": "228.692"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s like to me it&#39;s\nlike Newton&#39;s Law,", 
            "dur": "1.78", 
            "start": "233.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for every action there is an\nequal and opposite reaction.", 
            "dur": "3.45", 
            "start": "235.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Equal and opposite.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "238.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I think the\ngreater our sorrow is,", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "240.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the greater our\ncapacity is to feel joy.", 
            "dur": "2.75", 
            "start": "243.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve been surprised.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "246.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I feel a great deal of\ntenderness toward my Savior,", 
            "dur": "10.23", 
            "start": "248.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because He really is so sweet.", 
            "dur": "5.856", 
            "start": "258.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He really does\nprovide what you need.", 
            "dur": "3.624", 
            "start": "264.616"
        }
    ], 
